The Yu-Gi-Oh! TRADING CARD GAME takes Duelists through a futuristic supercharged journey to the past in Legendary Collection 5D’s, the latest entry in the popular Legendary Collection series.

Featuring over 250 of the most famous cards of the 5D’s era, Legendary Collection 5D’s gives Turbo Dueling the Mega-Pack treatment with 9 cards per pack (1 Secret Rare, 1 Ultra Rare, 1 Super Rare, 1 Rare, and 5 Commons). That’s 3 foil cards guaranteed per pack, with 5 packs per box.
